<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Rules of Love | VenusFrame</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Rules of Love</h1>

  <h2>Enter a Game ID of your choice and one of the three options considering the rules below.
      If a player has started game with that ID is in session, you will be matched with them.
      Otherwise, you will start a new game and someone else can enter your games ID to play against you.</h2>

  <h3>Rules</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Hard Candy Heart - Crushes Candle, Ignored in Favor of Box of Chocolates</li>
    <li>Box of Chocolates - Picked Over Candy Heart, Melted by Candle</li>
    <li>Candle - Melts Box of Chocolates, Crushed by Hard Candy Heart</li>
  </ul>

  <form method = "POST" action = "/games/rulesoflove/<%=gameId%>">
    <label for = "gameId"></label>
    <input name = "gameId" id = "gameId" class = "text" placeholder = "Game ID" type = "text" required>

    <div>
      <input type="radio" id="rolChoice" name="rolChoice" value="rolChoice" />
      <label for="rolChoice">Hard Candy Heart</label>

      <input type="radio" id="rolChoice" name="rolChoice" value="rolChoice" />
      <label for="rolChoice">Box of Chocolates</label>

      <input type="radio" id="rolChoice" name="rolChoice" value="rolChoice" />
      <label for="rolChoice">Candle</label>
    </div>

    <button class = "btn">PLAY</button>

</body>
</html>
